00:22:06.521 --> 00:22:09.752
Don't tell me
you are suspicious of me.

00:22:09.958 --> 00:22:14.622
I'm shocked. I, Hajime Fukuroda,
have devoted my entire being...

00:22:14.830 --> 00:22:19.961
