00:24:02.753 --> 00:24:06.917
Open your eyes and open the door

00:24:07.692 --> 00:24:12.129
The world in front of your eyes

00:24:12.897 --> 00:24:17.732
I want to go out
With my favorite sounds

00:24:18.102 --> 00:24:22.334
