00:24:23.574 --> 00:24:33.142
I'm here to enjoy the sunlight

00:24:33.718 --> 00:24:43.150
I'm enjoying myself
More than in the past

00:24:43.327 --> 00:24:47.559
I want to see you, but I can't

00:24:47.798 --> 00:24:52.633
So I just embrace my love

00:24:52.903 --> 00:24:57.738
Even walking on a crowded street

00:24:57.975 --> 00:25:04.312
Your smile makes my head spin

